channel.title: Continuously logging out
channel.description: Weird thing iam experiencing with some scripts. Every 4-10 mins iam reconnecting almost like it idles out while its not. Its not proxy issue cuz /em2() runs just fine on that proxy. Scripts i was using noobTrain and Karamja fisher/banker by taios. Any ide what the problem is? ty
